miami they were convicted in hastings court of skimming from a 
teamsters union pension fund loan 
in return hastings and borders were to receive 150000 
the romano brothers both of whom have since died refused to pay 
any bribe but the fbi mounted a stingtype operation and arrested 
borders pulling out of a suburban virginia motel with a garment bag 
containing 125000 handed to him by an undercover agent 
masquerading as frank romano 
borders was convicted of conspiracy and went to prison 
the house voted the articles of impeachment 4133 on aug 3 
