simply was not wellliked i dont believe that is a criteria to be 
used for whether the president ought to have the right to have his 
person as secretary of defense 
quayle also defended the new administrations pace which has 
been criticized as too slow 
were succeeding an administration of our own party at a time 
when the country is in good shape so were certainly not going 
to be stampeded into doing things for the sake of doing them soon 
or quickly or to show momentum or some such thing 
quick fixes are often bad fixes quayle added 
quayle also criticized politicians frantic efforts to gain 
press attention but said he was not referring to the mediawise 
campaign that elected him and bush last fall 
he said the political process is distorted when the need to 
make the 7 oclock news can lead politicians to announce initiatives 
that really arent well thought out initiatives that might well 
make the headlines but might not be very good for the health of the 
country 
asked about the bushquayle campaigns acknowledged management of 
the daily news packaging events and keeping the candidates away 
from reporters to keep from cluttering the canned message quayle 
said he was not talking about campaigns but added youve got a 
certain message you want to get across 
in his speech quayle said he was criticizing the way frantic 
efforts to gain press attention and produce sound bites can distort 
our political process by elevating form over substance and image 
over reality 
as to the blistering press reports about his own background that 
percolated throughout the campaign the vice president said he 
probably benefited from it in the long run he said the intense 
scrutiny was to be expected because he had been a littleknown 
senator outside his home state of indiana when bush picked him for a 
running mate 
youre an open target to criticism by your opposition that is 
the way we conduct our campaigns he said its healthy to see 
how one musters the scrutiny i believe i have emerged a stronger 
and better person because of it its an experience that had a 
meaningful purpose for me as being the vice president of the united 
states 
