showed it addressed to all uk airlines and el al air india 
us airlines south african airways 
the mirror said the notice advised security authorities to look 
for telltale signs that the instrument wouldnt play its insides 
would rattle the xray would show more wiring than usual and the 
antenna socket would be taped shut 
