<TEXT>
critics say the academy awards 
telecast is showing its age producer allan carr says thats the way 
it should be 
in an attempt to keep the programs ratings from slipping carr 
will celebrate oscar by reveling in its yesteryears 
im restoring it hopefully to what it was in its glorious 
day carr said of the march 29 broadcast of the 61st annual 
academy awards from the shrine auditorium in los angeles the 
program will be shown at 9 pm est by abctv 
carr and scenic designer ray clausen will recreate a likeness of 
the cocoanut grove the tropical nightclub where the oscar dinner 
banquet was held in 1940 famous movie couples will be seated at 
tables between the palm trees and a bandstand will be on the stage 
this is the ultimate variety show carr said its also the 
ultimate awards show that all the other awards show copy so i have 
to make this a return to oscar the way it was in the old days 
because now you have the tonys the grammys the american music 
awards the peoples choice awards theres an awards show on 
every other week 
the oscars are supposed to be really glamorous and fun its 
the highest awards we give our royalty in this country im going to 
shock people with glamour and humor 
carr comes from a career filled with flamboyant spectacles as 
the producer of the stage hit la cage aux folles and the movies 
grease cant stop the music and where the boys are 84 
his projects have rarely strayed from playfulness and overblown 
kitsch he even held a blacktie dinner party in 1976 at the lincoln 
heights jail in a rundown section of east los angeles to celebrate 
the opening of murder by death which starred the late author 
truman capote 
whether people like me or dont like me or they like what i do 
or dont like what i do they know that i love hollywood and im a 
big enthusiast for hollywood carr said 
for the last four years the orchestra has not been in the 
auditorium they were at an abc studio five miles away and the music 
was piped in but this is going to be a broadway show i insisted 
that the orchestra comes back marvin hamlisch will be in the pit 
conducting and ramps have been put over the orchestra pit so the 
people can run up the aisles 
i am producing really two things a live show for the people 
who are there like a broadway opening night and a television 
show which has a feeling of a broadway opening night for the people 
at home 
there will be no single program host this year don johnson and 
melanie griffith will present the first statuette cher and michael 
douglas will present the last and dozens of other stars will manage 
everything in between 
offscreen couples will be paired onscreen farrah fawcett will 
appear with ryan oneal goldie hawn will be with kurt russell and 
demi moore will be escorted by her husband bruce willis 
its like chariots of fire its like a relay race carr 
said the presenters pass the torch to the next person 
the telecast will honor awards presenters as well as winners 
when stewart and kim novak appear to hand out a trophy the audience 
will be shown a clip from their work together in 1958s vertigo 
the awards show will be held on wednesday this year unlike the 
traditional monday the move is a result of both the preceding 
