there will be a retrospective of film musicals 
i wanted to bring my love of the musical movie to the oscars 
carr said through lots of research i realized that more movie 
stars made musicals in the 50s than any other decade so i have put 
together this homage to the stars of the 50s musical and you will 
see people like betty grable gene kelly donald oconnor but 
also mario lanza elvis presley ava gardner rita hayworth and lana 
turner 
carr said complaints about past oscar shows running past their 
allotted three hours miss the real point 
you only realize how long it is if youre bored he said 
my answer is you didnt ask how long ben hur was now that 
lawrence of arabia is out again its almost four hours long no 
one complains if youre entertained you dont watch the clock 
to keep the pace brisk oscar winners with multiple trophy 
recipients as is common in technical awards will have one 
designated speaker after 30 seconds of thank yous the microphone 
will go dead and the camera will go to the next podium said carr 
they can talk as long as they want but no ones going to hear 
it 
