berkshire hathaway inc which is headed by 
investor warren buffett has accumulated since last summer a 63 
percent stake in cocacola co that is now valued at about 115 
billion coke has disclosed 
cocacola officials said they viewed the purchases as a strong 
vote of confidence from the widelyrespected investor who with 
his wife controls 45 percent of the omaha nebbased berkshire 
